text:
Tenka...
will do her best today...!

Ah... and there's something
I've been thinking about...

Today, I want to cheer up the
people who came to watch...!

Hehe... just like how Naa-chan
and Chiyuki-san gave me snacks...

Just like how Producer-san
encouraged me...!

...!
Yeah, I'm looking forward to it.
